fentra #oott\n\nNext two weeks we should have the results for the Pacassa SW drill\n\nThe major risk now is geology, with 60% chance of success.\n\nThe drill is in an untapped extension delimited by a clear structural fault that could have been filled by the same kitchen below https://t.co/zWW79mbL", "time": "09:02", "author": "Riccardino999", "author_name": "Mr Rhino", "followers": 1449, "views": 3167, "likes": 14, "replies": 2, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2068265519040348629", "url": "https://x.com/SpreadChartsCom/status/2068265519040348629", "text": "Maybe I’m blind 👀, but I don’t see the record Brent 🛢️ short positions everyone is freaking out about 🤔\n\nYes, speculative net positions have collapsed 📉\n\nBut most speculators are still net long 📊 (net traders), and retail remains fully invested ⚠️\n\n#OOTT $BNO $USO $XLE $XOP https://t.co/CvjVup6bao", "time": "09:31", "author": "SpreadChartsCom", "author_name": "SpreadCharts.com", "followers": 4362, "views": 1156, "likes": 10, "replies": 3, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2068282817004314706", "url": "https://x.com/piotrmiecz/status/2068282817004314706", "text": "Jeszcze miesiąc \"pokoju\" i braku ropy z bliskiego wschodu i zacznie się gigantyczny kryzys paliwowy.\n\nDane: Morgan Stanley\n\n#oott https://t.co/veCgZHKkz2", "time": "10:40", "author": "piotrmiecz", "author_name": "Piotr Mieczkowski TMT", "followers": 4099, "views": 1097, "likes": 11, "replies": 2, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2068302401937801495", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068302401937801495", "text": "China's May refined oil exports rise from April under restrictions, Australia receives agreed volume #oott https://t.co/9YVUpEkOgD", "time": "11:58", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 2966, "likes": 18, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2068307749495070817", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2068307749495070817", "text": "WTI futures are over-sold\n\nPrice fell $8.28 (10%) from $84.99 to $76.60 week ending June 19\n\n12-month spreads suggest sideways prices on Monday\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/ZLAGhWcZH0", "time": "12:19", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 4333, "likes": 43, "replies": 8, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2068308934868242913", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2068308934868242913", "text": "WTI  12-month spread narrowed $4.31 (38%) for the week ending June 19\n\n6-month spread narrowed $3.36 (45%) \n\nPrice fell $8.28 (10%) from $84.88 to $76.60\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/zAFMoJM0ys", "time": "12:24", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 2216, "likes": 17, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2068321067312062692", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2068321067312062692", "text": "#OOTT", "time": "13:12", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 1417, "likes": 4, "replies": 3, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2068322912902258894", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068322912902258894", "text": "Iran's Tasnim report Strait of Hormuz closed due to ceasefire violation #oott", "time": "13:19", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3230, "likes": 23, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2068323382915940543", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068323382915940543", "text": "\"Strait of Hormuz will be closed to all maritime traffic\" #oott", "time": "13:21", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4841, "likes": 28, "replies": 1, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2068324249647943785", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068324249647943785", "text": "The boss of #Iraq’s state oil-marketing company SOMO, Ali Nizar, said separately in an interview with Iraq 24 television that two ships are currently loading at the country’s southern terminal but that more would need to enter Hormuz for output to keep rising.\n#oott", "time": "13:25", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3694, "likes": 14, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iraq", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2068351287423320555", "url": "https://x.com/cbjom/status/2068351287423320555", "text": "I guess Team Iran has come to negotiate on everything  other than nukes.\n\n#OOTT", "time": "15:12", "author": "cbjom", "author_name": "Crudehead🛢", "followers": 17544, "views": 2732, "likes": 8, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2068379950269252046", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068379950269252046", "text": "IEA on SPR releases :\nApril release pace 2mbpd, May pace 2.5mbpd,\n252mb so far released, further scheduled releases 79mb\n #oott https://t.co/XMXilk4l6h", "time": "17:06", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 34617, "likes": 75, "replies": 7, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2068397928260284736", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2068397928260284736", "text": "Here is the SAR satellite imagery of the SoH dated June 20th. Zoom in and those white specks are your hulls. The traditional transit lanes are zero traffic. Every single ship on the tape is currently hugging the Iranian corridor.\n\n#oott #iran https://t.co/gLBdvWNY1g", "time": "18:17", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 46590, "likes": 215, "replies": 17, "retweets": 29, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 22, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2068404791219495210", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2068404791219495210", "text": "Oil exports are strictly a winner's game. \n\nOther GCC players can't even get normal loadings off the ground today, but Iran is out here concurrently loading three hulls over at Kharg. \n\nThen again, they're already on